        A complete WVO processing plant integrates multiple stages of treatment to handle the wide range of contaminant types and concentrations found in waste vegetable oil. The following describes a typical plant configuration. Also read about using a disc-stack centrifuge for <a href="/yellow-grease-purification-centrifuge/">yellow grease purification</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-[50%] shrink-0">
